                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7239" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0222</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9119 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">野蛮抑或文明：浙民投敌意并购ST生化的进攻与整合之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Barbarism or civilization: the way of attack and integration of Zhejiang Mintou&#39;s hostile acquisition of ST Biochemical</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李旎，姚俊生，许玉华</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广州大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ST生化（派林生物）</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">敌意并购；控制权市场；中小股东；治理效应</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hostile Takeover; Market of Corporate Control; Minority Shareholders; Governance Effect</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">控制权转移是资本市场发挥公司治理效应与约束内部人行为的重要机制。但实践中并购方可能在没有获取上市公司董事会同意的情况下发起敌意并购，引发控制权争夺战，危及上市公司持续稳定经营。本案例关注A股首例成功实施的市场化敌意并购——浙民投并购ST生化（现已更名为“派林生物”），介绍了控制权争夺前的背景，描述了作为进攻方的浙民投与作为防守方的原上市公司大股东振兴集团的攻守大战，展示了中小股东如何充分发挥水能载舟亦能覆舟的作用。在成功入主上市公司后，浙民投通过更换董监高、剥离不良资产、引入战略投资者与产业并购等方式，逐步实现对上市公司的实质性控制，帮助上市公司增强在产业链上的话语权，改善公司经营效率。由此，控制权市场的治理效应得以充分体现。本案例有助于引导学生理解控制权争夺的途径与控制权变更后的整合，帮助他们深入理解控制权市场发挥治理效应的内在机制，并对监管层完善引导中小股东参与公司治理的制度具有启示意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The transfer of control is an important mechanism for the capital market to exert the effect of corporate governance and restrain the behavior of insiders. However, in practice, the acquirer may initiate a hostile takeover without the consent of the board of directors of the listed company, which leads to a battle for control and damages the sustainable operation of the listed company. This case focuses on the first successful market-oriented hostile takeover of A-share market—Zhejiang United Investment Group&#39;s M&amp;A of ST Zhenxing Biopharmaceutical and Chemical (now renamed “Paisishuanglin Bio-Pharmacy”). We introduce the background before the battle, describe the battle between Zhejiang United Investment Group as the attacker and Zhenxing Group, the former major shareholder of the listed company, as the defender, and shows how minority shareholders can give full play to the role that the water that bears the boat is the same that swallows it up. After successful becoming the owner of the listed company, Zhejiang United Investment Group has gradually achieved substantial control over the listed company by replacing the directors and supervisors, stripping off non-performing assets, introducing strategic investors and industrial M&amp;A, etc., which help the listed company enhance its impact in the supply chain and improve the company&#39;s operating efficiency. As a result, the governance effect of the control market is fully reflected. This case will be helpful to guide students to understand the paths of control battle and the integration after the change of control, helping them deeply understand the internal mechanism of the control market to exert governance effects. This case also has enlightened significance for regulators to improve the system that guides minority shareholders to engage in corporate governance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司理财》、《企业并购》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">敌意并购的动机；并购策略的选择；控制权防御机制与策略；反并购失败原因；并购后整合</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
